cs.NI, cs.IT, cs.COMM, cs.SY, cs.MA 

This paper is primarily focused on communication support for IoT devices, which falls under the category of networked and distributed systems (cs.NI). It also involves optimization of link parameters, which is related to information theory (cs.IT) and communication systems (cs.COMM). The use of a look-up table (LUT) is a common technique in control systems and optimization (cs.SY), and the experiments involve simulation and analysis, which could fall under machine learning (cs.MA).
